abstract: >-
  S5-HES Agent is an agentic RAG-enhanced framework for simulating smart home
  environments with integrated IoT security analysis. It combines multi-provider
  LLM orchestration, hybrid retrieval-augmented generation, realistic device and
  behavioral simulation, and MITRE ATT&CK-aligned threat modeling to provide a
  comprehensive platform for smart home security research.
